    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Vic</abbr><ex cert="low">cius</ex></expan> Seneca <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>ues</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXII <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>rimigeniae</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>Ant</abbr><ex>oninianae</ex></expan></del> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> e<lb break="no" n="3"/>x voto in suo po<lb break="no" n="4"/>su<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>t Grato et Se<lb break="no" n="5"/>leugo <note>sic</note> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> pri<lb break="no" n="6"/>die <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Mart</abbr><ex>ias</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Jupitergigantensäule; Gesamthöhe nur ungefähr. Die Inschrift befindet sich auf dem Viergötterstein (Z. 1 auf dessen corona); auf den Nebenseiten und der Rückseite Darstellungen von Mercur, Minerva und Hercules. (B): Prost; AE 1894: Z. 3: P(rimigeniae) p(iae); Bauchhenß: Z. 3: Ant(oninianae); Prost; AE 1894; CIL 13, 07609; Bauchhenß: Z. 4/5: po/suit; Mattern: Z. 4/5: po/s[ui]t; Prost; AE 1894: Z. 5/6: Se/leuco.</p>
            </div>
